{
  "name": "1 - Main Triage Agent (v2)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Main Triage Agent v2\n\nAdds to v1:\n- Checks 'Sender Preferences' before logging a promo sender (never re-asks about a decided sender)\n- Detects subscription/appointment dates, dedupes against 'Subscriptions Tracker', creates/updates Google Calendar events with 2-day-before + day-of reminders\n\n**Sheets needed (same spreadsheet, different tabs):**\n`Processed Log`, `Promo Mentions This Week`, `Sender Preferences`, `Subscriptions Tracker`\n\nFill in [[BRACKETED]] placeholders before running: Gmail cred, Anthropic key, label IDs, Sheet ID, Calendar ID, Telegram cred/chat.",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 380
      },
      "id": "4d15ebe0-f26d-4125-87b8-657c609f2680",
      "name": "Overview1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -2816,
        1552
      ]
    },
